California Pizza Kitchen Investor Lawsuit Calls $470 Million Bid Too Low

-- B y   P h i l   M i l f o r d
-- 
2011-06-10T18:35:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-10/california-pizza-kitchen-investor-lawsuit-calls-470-million-bid-too-low.html
California Pizza Kitchen Inc. (CPKI) , the
restaurant chain being taken over by Golden Gate Capital Corp.,
was sued today in Delaware Chancery Court by an investor who
contends the company is worth more than the $470 million,
$18.50-a-share offer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Phil Milford in Wilmington, Delaware at 
 pmilford@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
